title: FOCUS, GET THINGS DONE & HAVE A BREAK WITH EddieHub + Centered
description: Do you keep getting distracted and not finishing your tasks?  Maybe you are a project maintainer and need to get through your GitHub notifications, you might be freelancing for a client or you might have course work or exam preparation to do. Let's get totally absorbed in our tasks together and be more productive, with the help of Centered! When it is time for a break, we will jump on an exclusive Discord audio call and chat.
